latestIgtvVideos.title: Manufacturing of Gemstones
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Introducing the whole process of manufacturing of gemstones from mines to the market. 

The first step is procuring Rough (Raw Material) then Assorting the rough based on the requirement. Master craftsman marks stone to cut then it goes onto the hands of Skilled artisans for Pre Forming,  Calibration and Polishing. Finally the finished gemstones go into jewellery. 

Isn’t it fabulous to know how beautiful gemstones are form!

Comment below to know more.
#gemstonesworld #manufaturingindustry #aquamarine #emerald #ruby #tourmaline #jewelrydesigner # jeweleryworld
